# B2 counterpart: a TRUE first install (no hook file exists at all) still announces
# itself — the messages are for real first-time setup, not build updates.
desc quiet heal: true first install still shows the install messages, log says first_install=1
invoke launch
config paired
seeded
pick 2|
expect_exit 0
expect_trace PRES timeout=-1 msg='Installing Lodor...'
expect_log hooks self-installed + verified (first_install=1)
